title: Colton Underwood Gives Bobby Bachelor Advice + Chris Janson Stops By

description:
Colton Underwood calls in and gives Bobby some hypothetical advice on being The Bachelor. Chris Janson stops by and talks about starting a business with Lunchbox. Also, the show shares their first celebrity crushes.
